---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Pricing — Job Red Flag Detector — Zurhaar Tools" description="Scan job postings for red flags. One-time credit packs starting at €1.99.">
  <section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16">
    <div class="text-center mb-14">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium text-primary-light mb-3 tracking-wide uppercase">Job Red Flag Detector</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-4">Pay per scan. No subscription.</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-text-muted max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Buy a pack of scans and use them whenever you want. Credits never expire.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Pricing cards -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <!-- 50 scans -->
      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col hover:border-border-hover transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-1">Starter</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-4">50 scans</p>
        <div class="mb-6">
          <span class="text-3xl font-bold">€1.99</span>
          <span class="text-text-muted text-sm ml-1">one-time</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-text-muted mb-6 flex-1">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-400">&#10003;</span> 50 job posting scans
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-400">&#10003;</span> Credits never expire
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-400">&#10003;</span> All job sites supported
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a
          href="https://buy.stripe.com/test_fZucMY8I8fE0bpP6WU4gg00"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-text-muted border border-border hover:border-border-hover hover:text-text rounded-lg transition-all"
        >
          Get Started
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- 150 scans (popular) -->
      <div class="bg-card border-2 border-primary/50 rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col relative hover:border-primary transition-all">
        <span class="absolute -top-3 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 px-3 py-0.5 text-xs font-medium bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent text-white rounded-full">Best value</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-1">Standard</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-4">150 scans</p>
        <div class="mb-6">
          <span class="text-3xl font-bold">€4.99</span>
          <span class="text-text-muted text-sm ml-1">one-time</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-text-muted mb-6 flex-1">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-400">&#10003;</span> 150 job posting scans
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-400">&#10003;</span> Credits never expire
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-400">&#10003;</span> All job sites supported
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a
          href="https://buy.stripe.com/test_7sY7sEcYobnKfG52GE4gg01"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-accent hover:opacity-90 rounded-lg transition-opacity"
        >
          Get Started
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- 500 scans -->
      <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-xl p-6 flex flex-col hover:border-border-hover transition-all">
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-1">Pro</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-text-muted mb-4">500 scans</p>
        <div class="mb-6">
          <span class="text-3xl font-bold">€9.99</span>
          <span class="text-text-muted text-sm ml-1">one-time</span>
        </div>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-text-muted mb-6 flex-1">
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-400">&#10003;</span> 500 job posting scans
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-400">&#10003;</span> Credits never expire
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="text-green-400">&#10003;</span> All job sites supported
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a
          href="https://buy.stripe.com/test_14A14g5vW1Na0Lb0yw4gg02"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-medium text-text-muted border border-border hover:border-border-hover hover:text-text rounded-lg transition-all"
        >
          Get Started
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- How it works -->
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8">How it works</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-accent/20 border border-primary/20 text-primary-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-sm font-bold">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Buy a scan pack</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Choose a pack above. You'll receive a license key by email instantly.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-accent/20 border border-primary/20 text-primary-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-sm font-bold">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Install the extension</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Get the Job Red Flag Detector from the Chrome Web Store and enter your license key.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
          <div class="w-8 h-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/20 to-accent/20 border border-primary/20 text-primary-light rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 text-sm font-bold">3</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold mb-1">Scan any job posting</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Open a job listing on any site, click Scan, and get an instant red flag analysis with a score out of 10.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-center mb-8">Questions</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Do credits expire?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">No. Your credits stay on your account until you use them.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Can I buy more scans later?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Yes. Additional purchases are added to your existing balance automatically.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">Which job sites are supported?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">LinkedIn, Indeed, Glassdoor, StepStone, Monster, Reed, SEEK, Nationale Vacaturebank, and most other job sites.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold mb-2">What does a scan include?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-text-muted">Each scan gives you a score out of 10, a list of red flags (vague salary, unrealistic requirements, toxic culture signals), and green flags — with explanations for each.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
